OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will stay
OL,6,Fcloudier in the west with scattered
OL,7,Fshowers feeding in. Generally drier
OL,8,Fwith some bright then clear spells in
OL,9,Fthe east. Windy at times.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSaturday:FSome dry and bright spells
OL,12,Fat first. Otherwise largely cloudy
OL,13,Fwith showers, heavy at times,
OL,14,Fgradually easing later in the day.
OL,15,FWindy at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
