OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FMostly
OL,6,Fdry and increasingly sunny on Sunday,
OL,7,Fthe odd light shower at first. Dry and
OL,8,Fbright on Monday. Mostly cloudy
OL,9,FTuesday with rain or showers. Becoming
OL,10,Fwarmer.
